judiciously managing resources with structured inputs in the domains of project planning, scheduling and monitoring
to ensure project accomplishment within defined time/cost parameters.
✓ Possess flair for drawing, deft in translating concepts, dexterous in visualizing accurately have an eye for detail with
the ability to function independently as well as in a team.
Core Competencies:-
Architectural Design & Drawing  Civil & Structural Drafting  Site Administration  Civil/Interior/Exterior works.
Computer proficiency:-
Packages know:-
• AutoCAD (2004,2006, 2009,2012,2014,2015,2018 & 3D Civil), SP3D Smart plant, Sketchup Pro & MS Office.
