Headline: Executive Summary

Employment: (1) Company: Acciona-Gulermak CWJV
Duration: June.2017 to 31 May 2019.
Designation: Sr. Surveyor
Project :Design and build the extension of Dubai’s Red metro line and upgrade the system
of the existing line. The total value of the project, also called Route 2020, is €2.6 billion.
Alstom’s share represents half [1] and the civil works, led by ACCIONA including
Gulermak, represent the other half. The extended line, which will connect the city to the
Expo 2020 site, is expected to start commercial service in 2020 for the World Expo [2].
The project involves the construction of a 15-kilometre-long line – of which 11.8
kilometers of elevated metro line and 3.2 kilometers underground metro line - branching
off the existing red line at the Nakheel Harbour & Tower station. The metro extension will
have seven stations, including an interchange at Nakheel Harbour and an iconic metro
station at the World Expo site. The highly-complex project will include a 3.2 km tunnel
perforated by a tunnel boring machine, 1.2 km of open-cut route and 11.8 km of elevated
viaduct metro line.
Client: RTA.
-- 1 of 8 --
Responsibilities:
● Establishment of Surface control network and jointly check .
● Layout of columns, Piers, Piling & Launching of segments.
● Drawing study and calculation required data.
● Responsible for managing the activities of the surveying department. This includes use of instruments such
as total stations, levels, download survey data, survey calculations, problem solving and maintain the high
accuracy of the projects.
● Maintain the documents details and making a file for the internal and external Audit.
● Advance Planning for the Survey work to achieve the weekly and monthly task.
● Marking of Guide wall and D wall for Cut & Cover and Prop Beams, intermediate Prop Beams
,Electrical Room,Base Slab ,Track bed, capping Beam,Parapet walls & Openings.
● Ability to conduct from TBM Launching to breakthrough all Survey Tunnel work (like- Credal fixing,eyeseal
fixing,TBM alignment,Laser shifting, wriggle survey, control point shifting inside shaft and tunnel etc.).
● Launching of TBM and solving the Guidance system (VMT) issue and tunnel all Survey issue.
(2) Company: M/s Pratibha Industries Ltd.
Duration: Aug.2014 to June 2017.
Designation: Sr. Surveyor
Project: Design and Construction of Tunnel between Hauz Khas Station and Kalkaji Station
By Shield TBM, Tunnel near Chirag delhi & Kalkaji Station and Underground Ramp beyond
Kalkaji station by Cut & Cover Method , Underground Metro Station at Panchsheel Park,
Chirag Delhi, G.K. Enclave-1, Nehru Place & Kalkaji by Cut & Cover Method on Janakpuri
West-Botanical Garden Corridor of of Delhi MRTS Project on Phase-III.
Client: Delhi Metro Rail Corporation.
Type of Work: Construction of tunnel by TBM with Guidance system VMT for Harrenknetch TBM
and ENZAN for THI TBM Station by Cut & Cover method.
Responsibilities:
● Establishment of Tunnel control network and Surface control network and jointly check .

